\f0\b\fs24 \cf0 About\
\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\tx7200\ql\qnatural

\f1\b0 \cf0 \
This is a Mach-O version of MacCvs. It is named MacCvsX, and it works with Mac OS X 10.1 or later.\
\
This program implements the CvsGui User Interface on top of cvs .\
\
\
\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\tx7200\ql\qnatural

