\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\tx7200\ql\qnatural

\f1\b0 \cf0 \
Just drag the folder 
\f2 MacCvsX-3.3a2
\f1  to the place on your harddisk where you want to keep it.\
Inside the folder, you'll find the following items:
